作者：匡达“ 疫情尚未结束，但生活还得继续。
Authors: "The epidemic is not over yet, but life must continue."
”目前，我国对新冠肺炎疫情的防控已进入关键时刻。
"At present, China's new crown pneumonia epidemic prevention and control has entered a critical moment.
据上海国际问题研究院14日发布的报告评估，全国疫情发展趋势继续企稳向好，整体疫情拐点的出现时间，将取决于中国目前采取的防疫举措的落地和全体民众的配合程度。
According to a report released on the 14th by the Shanghai Institute of International Studies, the trend of national epidemic continues to stabilize, and the overall inflection point will depend on China's current epidemic prevention initiatives and the degree of cooperation of the entire population.
疫情笼罩下的周末，京沪两地出门的人依然稀少。
During the weekend of the epidemic, few people left their homes in Beijing or Shanghai.
居民佩戴口罩，外出采购必要的生活用品和接收快递。
Residents wear masks, go out to purchase essential supplies and receive couriers.
在记者所在的北京市海淀区花园路街道小关社区，社区街道已实施封闭式管理，进出的人和车辆都需出示临时出入证和车证。
In the neighborhood of Xiaoguan Street, Huayuan Road, Haidian District, Beijing, where the reporters are located, community streets are under closed management and people and vehicles entering and leaving the area are required to present temporary passes and identification cards.
各个小区大门封闭，只保留一个出入口。
Each cell gate is closed, leaving only one entrance and exit.
基本食品和部分生活用品可以在社区街道的超市完成采购。
Basic food items and some household items can be purchased at a supermarket on a community street.
2020年2月15日，北京，今冬第七场大雪过后，周六开始放晴，居民外出采购蔬菜、84消毒液等生活用品。
February 15, 2020, Beijing, this winter after the seventh snowfall, Saturday began to clear up, residents out shopping vegetables, 84 disinfectant and other daily necessities.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，居民下楼遛狗。
Photo: Quanda 2020 Sunday, Feb. 16, Beijing, residents walk their dogs downstairs.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，走在街道上的市民均佩戴口罩。
Photo: Hong Da On Sunday, February 16, 2020, Beijing, people walking in the streets are wearing masks.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，城管执勤岗亭前的电子屏幕滚动播放文字，提醒民众戴口罩、勤洗手等防疫基本知识。
Photo: Quanda February 16, 2020, Beijing, the city guard post in front of the electronic screen rolling text, to remind people to wear masks, wash their hands and other basic epidemic prevention knowledge.
摄影：匡达2020年2月15日周六，上海，闵行区金汇路一个小区的大门已封闭，门口挂着宣传标语。
Photo: Quanda 2020 February 15, 2020, Shanghai, Minhang District Jinhui Road, a small area of the door has been closed, hung at the door of the poster.
摄影：范剑磊2020年2月15日周六，北京，小关西后街已实施封闭式管理，管理员正在将门拉上。
Photo: Fan Jianlei Saturday, Feb. 15, 2020, Beijing, small Kansai Houjie has been closed management, the administrator is pulling the door.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，小区的一处大门已临时关闭，每个小区只留一个门口进出。
Photo: Quanda February 16, 2020, Beijing, a small community door has been temporarily closed, leaving only one door in and out of each.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，小关社区街道上的一家超市正在营业，店员和顾客均佩戴口罩。
Photo: Quanta On Sunday, Feb. 16, 2020, a supermarket opens on the streets of Xiaoguan community in Beijing. Shop assistants and customers wear masks.
摄影：匡达2020年2月15日周六，北京，一位女士戴着口罩拖着购物车走在人行道上。
Photo: Quanta On Saturday, Feb. 15, 2020, a woman walks down the sidewalk with a shopping cart wearing a mask.
摄影：匡达2020年2月15日周六，北京，用电动车托运物资的居民。
Photo: Hong Da 2020 February 15, 2020, Beijing, with electric vehicles consigned goods residents.
为减少出门次数，人们都尽量一次性采购足够多的生活物资。
To reduce the number of trips, people try to buy enough supplies at a time.
摄影：匡达2020年2月15日周六，上海，闵行区金汇路盒马鲜生物流中心外，两名外卖小哥正准备出发。
Photo: Quanda 2020 February 15, 2020, Shanghai, Minhang District Jinhui Road Box Ma Xian Biology Flow Center, outside, two small brothers are ready to leave.
摄影：范剑磊2020年2月15日周六，北京，一位男士手捧一大袋药品，走在居民小区内。
Photo: Fan Jianlei On Saturday, Feb. 15, 2020, a man walks in a residential area carrying a large bag of medicine.
摄影：匡达2020年2月15日周六，北京，小关街道封闭出入口外侧，快递小哥正在为居民查找快递。
Photo: Quanda February 15, 2020, Beijing, Xiaoguan Street closed the outside of the entrance, express brother is looking for express delivery for residents.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，小关社区街道上，佩戴口罩行走的居民。
Photo: Quanda 2020 February 16, 2020, Beijing, Xiaoguan community streets, wearing masks on the residents.
摄影：匡达2020年2月15日周六，上海，雨中一辆电动车停在闵行区金汇路银行门口，驾驶员佩戴口罩。
Photo: Kuanda February 15, 2020, Shanghai, rain in an electric vehicle parked in Minhang District Jinhui Road bank door, driver wearing masks.
摄影：范剑磊2020年2月15日周六，北京，小关社区街道上，正在巡逻的警车。
Photo: Fan Jianlei On Saturday, Feb. 15, 2020, police cars patrol the streets of Xiaoguan community in Beijing.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，居民楼的电梯内贴着通知，要求住户配合疫情防控办理出入证和车证。
Photo: Quanda February 16, 2020, Beijing, residents of the elevator notice in the building to cooperate in the prevention and control of the epidemic for pass and license.
摄影：匡达2020年2月16日周日，北京，小关社区街道封闭出入口的工作人员正在检查来往车辆和居民的车证和出入证。
Photo: Quanta On Sunday, Feb. 16, 2020, workers at the closed entrances to the streets of Xiaoguan neighborhood in Beijing are checking cars and residents' identification and passes.
